title: The Green Yard Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Indian, International, Italian, Japanese, Thai, Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bistro offering sandwiches, salads, a daily-changing menu including international and local dishes, and cakes. Vegan options may include soup, hummus sandwich, rice and vegetable dishes, soya goulash. Uses local ingredients where possible.
